  "notes": "* <i>Death Surge</i> will grant the bonus movement speed after a brief delay.\n<ul><li><ul><li>The buff is intended to grant 75% decaying movement speed, but instead grants 67% movement speed decaying with -8% per stat update.\n<ul><li>Precisely this leaves him at <span data-bot_key=\"%\" style=\"position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;\" data-top_label=\"time passed\" data-displayformula=\"67% after 0 to 0.32 seconds, then &nbsp;−&nbsp;8% per stat update\" data-bot_values=\"0;67;59;51;43;35;27;19;11;3;0\" class=\"pp-tooltip\" data-top_values=\"0;0.26;0.53;0.79;1.06;1.32;1.58;1.85;2.11;2.38;2.64\">0% − 0% (based on time passed)</span> bonus movement speed.</li></ul></li></ul></li>\n<li><i>Death Surge</i> has a shared cooldown across each ability key, regardless of which key is used to activate it. Thus, activating <i>Death Surge</i> with any ability key will put the others on cooldown.</li>\n<li><i>Death Surge's</i> cooldown resets upon death.</li>\n<li><i>Death Surge's</i> cooldown is affected by <span style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><a title=\"Ability haste\" href=\"/wiki/Ability_haste\"><img data-image-name=\"Cooldown reduction icon.png\" alt=\"Cooldown reduction icon\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"15\" decoding=\"async\" data-relevant=\"0\" width=\"15\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/95/Cooldown_reduction_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203444\" data-image-key=\"Cooldown_reduction_icon.png\" class=\"lazyload\"></a>&nbsp;ability haste</span> and thus the ability is technically able to be used up to twice during a single instance of <i>Glory in Death</i>, but this isn't practical.\n<ul><li><i>Death Surge</i> is not affected by <span class=\"inline-image label-after rune-icon\" data-param=\"\" style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\" data-rune=\"Ultimate Hunter\" data-game=\"lol\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\" data-width=\"20\"><a href=\"/wiki/Ultimate_Hunter_(Rune)\" title=\"Ultimate Hunter\"><img class=\"lazyload\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" data-relevant=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-name=\"Ultimate Hunter rune.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e4/Ultimate_Hunter_rune.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180509080323\" data-image-key=\"Ultimate_Hunter_rune.png\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" alt=\"Ultimate Hunter\"></a></span> <span style=\"word-break: keep-all;;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Ultimate_Hunter_(Rune)\" title=\"Ultimate Hunter (Rune)\" class=\"mw-redirect\">Ultimate Hunter</a></span></span>, even if cast from the ultimate ability slot.</li>\n<li>Despite showing the cooldown being reduced, <i>Death Surge</i> in the ultimate ability slot will be not reduced by <span data-param=\"\" data-item=\"Axiom Arc\" class=\"inline-image label-after item-icon\" data-game=\"lol\" style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\" data-width=\"20\" class=\"border\"><a title=\"Axiom Arc's\" href=\"/wiki/Axiom_Arc\"><img width=\"20\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"20\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" alt=\"Axiom Arc's\" class=\"thumbborder lazyload\" data-image-key=\"Axiom_Arc_item.png\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-name=\"Axiom Arc item.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/03/Axiom_Arc_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20211020233329\"></a></span> <span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Axiom_Arc\" title=\"Axiom Arc\">Axiom Arc's</a></span></span> <a href=\"/wiki/Named_item_effect#Flux\" title=\"Named item effect\">Flux</a> on <span class=\"glossary\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Takedown\"><a title=\"Takedown\" href=\"/wiki/Takedown\"><img data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/07/Damage_rating.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170514053710\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"20\" decoding=\"async\" data-image-name=\"Damage rating.png\" width=\"20\" class=\"lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-image-key=\"Damage_rating.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" alt=\"Damage rating\"></a> <a title=\"Takedown\" href=\"/wiki/Takedown\">takedown</a></span>.<sup><span style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;\" title=\"This is not intended.\" class=\"basic-tooltip\">(bug)</span></sup></li>\n<li><i>Death Surge's</i> cooldown is not reduced by <span style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\" data-param=\"\" class=\"inline-image label-after item-icon\" data-game=\"lol\" data-item=\"Navori Quickblades\"><span data-width=\"20\" class=\"border\" style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Navori_Quickblades\" title=\"Navori Quickblades'\"><img data-image-name=\"Navori Quickblades item.png\" data-image-key=\"Navori_Quickblades_item.png\" height=\"20\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e6/Navori_Quickblades_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201029200723\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" class=\"thumbborder lazyload\" alt=\"Navori Quickblades'\"></a></span> <span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Navori_Quickblades\" title=\"Navori Quickblades\">Navori Quickblades'</a></span></span> <a href=\"/wiki/Named_item_effect#Deft_Strike\" title=\"Named item effect\">Deft Strike</a>.</li></ul></li></ul>",
