      "description": "If <i>Decimating Smash</i> was charged for at least 1 second, <b>Sion</b> instead slams his axe down in the target direction, dealing <span style=\"color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal\">physical damage</span> to enemies hit, <span data-game=\"lol\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-tip=\"Airborne\" class=\"glossary\"><a title=\"Airborne\" href=\"/wiki/Airborne\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" width=\"20\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d6/Airborne_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201223933\" height=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Airborne icon.png\" data-image-key=\"Airborne_icon.png\" alt=\"Airborne icon\" data-relevant=\"0\" class=\"lazyload\"></a> <a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"/wiki/Airborne\" title=\"Airborne\">knocking them up</a></span> for <span class=\"pp-tooltip\" data-bot_values=\"0.5;0.63;0.75;0.88;1\" data-top_values=\"1;1.25;1.5;1.75;2\" data-displayformula=\"0.5+(0.125 every 0.25 seconds). ''Calculation starts at the first second.''\" style=\"position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;\" data-top_label=\"channel time\">0.<small>5</small> − 1 (based on channel time)</span> seconds, and <span data-game=\"lol\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-tip=\"Stun\" class=\"glossary\"><a href=\"/wiki/Stun\" title=\"Stun\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" data-relevant=\"0\" alt=\"Stun icon\" data-image-name=\"Stun icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/9d/Stun_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201223940\" data-image-key=\"Stun_icon.png\" height=\"20\"></a> <a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"/wiki/Stun\" title=\"Stun\">stunning</a></span> them for <span class=\"pp-tooltip\" data-top_label=\"channel time\" style=\"position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;\" data-bot_values=\"1.25;1.5;1.75;2;2.25\" data-displayformula=\"1.25+(0.25 every 0.25 seconds). ''Calculation starts at the first second.''\" data-top_values=\"1;1.25;1.5;1.75;2\">1.<small>25</small> − 2.<small>25</small> (based on channel time)</span> seconds.",
