  "notes": "* Minions or monsters that are flung away are immune to minion damage and take their damage once they are stopped if they would die to <i>Roar of the Slayer's</i> damage, by either colliding with terrain, reaching the end of their trajectory, or having their displacement interrupted.\n<ul><li>Unlike the intial single-target <a href=\"/wiki/Projectile\" title=\"Projectile\">projectile</a>, a thrown minion or monster is not blocked by <span data-param=\"\" class=\"inline-image label-after ability-icon\" style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\" data-ability=\"Wind Wall\" data-game=\"lol\" data-champion=\"Yasuo\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\" data-width=\"20\" class=\"border\"><a title=\"Wind Wall\" href=\"/wiki/Yasuo/LoL#Wind_Wall\"><img data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/2c/Yasuo_Wind_Wall.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20131122024151\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" class=\"thumbborder lazyload\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Wind Wall\" height=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Yasuo Wind Wall.png\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-key=\"Yasuo_Wind_Wall.png\" width=\"20\" data-relevant=\"0\"></a></span> <span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Yasuo/LoL#Wind_Wall\" title=\"Yasuo/LoL\">Wind Wall</a></span></span> or <span data-champion=\"Braum\" data-game=\"lol\" class=\"inline-image label-after ability-icon\" data-param=\"\" style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\" data-ability=\"Unbreakable\"><span data-width=\"20\" style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\" class=\"border\"><a href=\"/wiki/Braum/LoL#Unbreakable\" title=\"Unbreakable\"><img data-image-name=\"Braum Unbreakable.png\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" alt=\"Unbreakable\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/3f/Braum_Unbreakable.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170818001617\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-image-key=\"Braum_Unbreakable.png\" class=\"thumbborder lazyload\"></a></span> <span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a title=\"Braum/LoL\" href=\"/wiki/Braum/LoL#Unbreakable\">Unbreakable</a></span></span>.</li>\n<li>Gaining or losing <span style=\"color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal\">AP</span>, or upgrading the ability while its projectile is traveling will change its damage for every future hit. This applies to both the intial single-target projectile, as well as the minion-projectile.</li>\n<li>This ability will cast from wherever the caster is at the end of the cast time.</li></ul>",
